(f) In 1994-95 new arrangements for the administration of the program are being implemented. This will entail the Commonwealth paying its contribution to the program to the Office of the Murray-Darling Basin Commission rather than as has previously been the case directly to the relevant State Government. Acquittal arrangements will be based on those outlined under clauses 70 and 71 of the Murray-Darling Basin Agreement (a schedule to the

 Murray-Darling Basin Act 1993

). There are no outstanding acquittals.
